title: If your time, energy and/or information were not enough, it's not your fault.
pid: 58aa2e6d-e07c-4adb-bc53-c9a569084529
body: |2-
  Only if you made dumb choices could feeling bad about it
  serve a useful (learning) purpose.
  And even if your choices look dumb,
  they may have been perfect given what you believed.
misc:
- Had_ID_Before_Import
